The purpose of the Partnership is to engage in the following business:

{{business_purpose}}

The principal place of business of the Partnership shall be {{principal_place_of_business}}. The Partnership may also conduct business at such other locations as the Partners may agree upon from time to time.

Each Partner shall make the following initial capital contributions to the Partnership:

- {{partner_1_name}}: ${{partner_1_contribution}}
- {{partner_2_name}}: ${{partner_2_contribution}}

Additional capital contributions may be made by mutual agreement of the Partners. No Partner shall be required to make additional contributions without their consent.
